[SetUp "1"]

{ We reached a typical position in the Berlin with 4.d3. The Berlinner footprints can be discovered by the open f-file and the strong pawn phalanx a2-b2-c2-d3-e4. }
20. Rh4 f6 21. Qg6 Qf7 22. Qg3 Nb4 { 22...Kh7  23.Ng5+! } 23. Bxh6 Nxc2 24. Ne5
fxe5 25. Rxf7 Rxf7 26. Qg6 Bxa2 27. Bg5 Rff8 28. Rh7 Rf7 29. Bf6
