12. Bc2
{ After Bb3, we are chased away by Nc5. Naturally, we are not allowed to give up our strong bishop. }
12... f5
{ This move loses a pawn since Black cannot take back because of a fork. } 13.
exf5 Rxf5 14. g4 { Simply losing a piece. } *

