{ Evidently, preserving our strong bishop. White is very flexible, as he can choose between different plans, amongst those: @@StartBracket@@1@@EndBracket@@ g2-g4 followed by Ng3, or @@StartBracket@@2@@EndBracket@@ undertaking action in the center with d3-d4. }
