{ This plan is occurring in several lines throughout this chapter. The knight on b7 is badly placed. }
15... Nb7 16. Qe2
{ discouraging a6-a5 since White can target the weak b5-pawn through Bd3, and preparing for a2-a4. White has secured a stable advantage. }
