b3
{ Meanwhile, White's mobilized pieces are ready for any hostile action in the center, White slowly tries to build up an initiative on the queenside. }
19... a5 20. d5 { The key idea of White's play on the queenside. } 20... Ne7
21. c4
{ the subtlety of the innocent-looking move b3 is revealed: Black can not break the white pawn chain. }
