{ Black's three main options here are: @@StartBracket@@1@@EndBracket@@  11...Be6  , @@StartBracket@@2@@EndBracket@@  11...Bd6  and @@StartBracket@@3@@EndBracket@@  11...Bc5  .    Before we delve into these theoretical and interesting positions, I would like to stress that there is not such a thing as an 'antidote' against these positions.  However, based on some strong ideas of the current leading players, we can get a grasp of the strategies involved and turn on the heat on our opponent maximally. }
