12... Bc5 13. Qe2
{ Black is about to make an important and difficult decision.  • Is he leaving the a-file for granted after  13...Rb8   • Is he giving up the c4-square with  13...b4   • or is he keeping the rook on a8 possibly sacrificing the b5-pawn? }
13... Ba7
{ So it's the latter.   Not much better would be  13...Rb8  . Play could continue  14.Nf1  Qc8  15.b4  Bd6  16.Bd3  with a slight edge for White. }
