16... Bxf3
{ 16...Be6  would lose a pawn after  17.Bxe6  Qxe6  18.Nxe5  Nxe5  19.Rxe5  and White is better. }
17. Qxf3 { Black is winning a pawn, but White is better developed. } 17... exd4
18. Bf4
