{ 1/2-1/2 @@StartBracket@@22@@EndBracket@@ Warmerdam,M @@StartBracket@@2497@@EndBracket@@ - Werle, J @@StartBracket@@2545@@EndBracket@@ Netherlands NED 2020.  Black is somewhat disorganized, whereas the fragile pawn on d6 is a matter of concern.  During the postmortem of this national competition game, the team of my opponent's team Apeldoorn @@StartBracket@@including GM's l'Ami and Warmerdam, as IM's Van Delft, Kuijpers and Oudeweetering@@EndBracket@@ analysed this position all the evening through. The 'communis opinio' was that Black was under heavy fire in the ensuing endings. }
